    public class MaterialRadioButton
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.RadioButton
implements HasGrid, HasType<RadioButtonType>
    Material Radio button has two types - NO-GAP
    - GAP

    UiBinder Usage:

     <m:MaterialRadioButton text="Sample"/>
 <m:MaterialRadioButton type="GAP"/>
    Author:
    kevzlou7979
